  pacing: "Pacing is a bit all over the place, as the movie feels incredibly slow in moments; some scenes were way longer than they needed to be, but sometimes they just breezed through the movie; the movie could have been cut by 5\342\200\22310 minutes by making some of the scenes shorter"
  climax: "Climax was pretty lackluster, as the movie felt like it overstayed its welcome in the final 20 minutes; The movie could have been cut by about 15 minutes to make the climax more tight"
  tone: "Tone is very unique as it is this hyper-pop glamorous feel that exaggerates Hollywood"
  final_notes: ""
